metadata.name: Algorithmic Genesis
metadata.description:
This generation is from a contract address I found while scrolling Twitter just 2 minutes after it deployed. Turning into a profitable trade during a time where my business is struggling due to factors out of my control. This generation represents seeing into a new world of opportunities.  
The prompt was the contract address that I made 2 eth + off of in 45 minutes. Saving my business. 

Genesis.
